": "ة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is affixed for the conversion of the word from an epithet to a subst.: (TA:) [pl. as above]. [It is also called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaqiyqapN", "text_ar": "حَقِيقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lugawiy~apN", "text_ar": "لُغَوِيَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaqiyqapN lugapF", "text_ar": "حَقِيقَةٌ لُغَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; to distinguish it from what is termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaqiyqapN Eurofiy~apN", "text_ar": "حَقِيقَةٌ عُرْفِيَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaqiyqapN EurofFA", "text_ar": "حَقِيقَةٌ عُرْفًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", which is"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A word,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "phrase, so much used in a particular tropical sense as to be, in that sense, conventionally regarded as proper;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as, for instance,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EadolN", "text_ar": "عَدْلٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the sense of “ just; ” it being properly an inf. n.] A"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "majaAz", "text_ar": "مَجَاز"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", when much used, becomes what is termed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaqiyqapN EurofFA", "text_ar": "حَقِيقَةٌ عُرْفًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (Mz 24th"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nwE", "text_ar": "نوع"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) ["}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaqiyqapN", "text_ar": "حَقِيقَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A proper"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(opposed to a tropical)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "signification."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]       -A3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlHaqiyqapu", "text_ar": "الحَقِيقَةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also signifies (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "That which,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "